These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, marigold
There 3 different types of food: apple, cherry, cucumber
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating apple is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsmarigold##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person eating cucumber is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Flower   | aconite     | amaryllis | marigold |
| Food   | cucumber  | apple    | cherry      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, july
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, comedy, thriller
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the fan of gospel and the person who's birthday is in july##2
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | october  | august     | july     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | comedy | disaster |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dannemann, old-henry
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, futuristic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the futuristic house and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar          | cain  | old-henry     | dannemann     |
| House           | futuristic | farmhouse  | gothic-revival   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

