.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, helicopter
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, sprite
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport    | airplane       | helicopter  | jet-ski   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Beverage   | sprite | water     | milk      |

