2. the owner of the bird is between the person driving the scooter and the analyst##2
3. the mechanic is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Job         | mechanic | architect | analyst |
| Transport   | scooter  | tram       | train       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

