.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, iced-tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dannemann, swisher
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the fan of country is between the person drinking lemonade and the dannemann-smoker##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Beverage          | lemonade | milk | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Cigar           | bongani      | swisher       | dannemann      |

