.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, librarian, doctor
City: london, colone, prague
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the librarian is between the person eating radish and the person driving the car##2
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the librarian is between the doctor and the person traveling to london##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | doctor |
| City   | london      | prague | colone   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

