2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the malaysian##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person watching sports movies##2
5. the person watching western movies is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel       | western      | sports      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | french-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | french          | thai       |

