2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the owner of the turtle is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
