There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | fanta | almond-milk |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop        | jazz            | r&b  |

