.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
3 different games are played: whist, scrabble, mah-jongg
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, scientific, drama
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Game      | mah-jongg     | scrabble | whist      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | scientific    | drama     |

