The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person drinking water is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who growszinnia##2
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person who growsrose is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water          | hot-chocolate |
| Flower          | zinnia | daffodil           | rose        |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | dog | goldfish         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

