City: berlin, new-york, san-francisco
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, spanish
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, subway, train
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the spanish##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person playing poker is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person playing go##2
5. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Game          | mah-jongg  | poker   | go |
| City   | san-francisco  | new-york     | berlin |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | spanish   |
| Transport     | train   | subway   | bike      |

