3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, epic, martial-arts
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
3. the lawyer is on the far left##1
4. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the chef##1
6. the chef is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
