There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, photography, puzzles
1. the german is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the egyptian##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person who likes turquise##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Color   | fuchsia | turquise  | red     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Hobby     | puzzles      | photography   | reading |

