2. the person playing go is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing domino##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes purple and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Color           | azure   | pink   | purple |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Game           | domino | go | bridge    |

