There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, lilac, yellow
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
There 3 different types of food: garlic, potato, blueberry
1. the person eating potato is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who likes ebony##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating garlic is between the person drinking milk and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Color         | lilac   | yellow | ebony |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Food           | blueberry           | garlic    | potato       |

