.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, ivory, lilac
City: nizza, colone, london
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person traveling to colone is the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the car##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person traveling to london is between the person driving the tram and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Color        | ivory      | pink | lilac |
| City         | colone     | london    | nizza        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 